ActCanada Pension Plan

SubjectTerms and Conditions - Revised Agreement on Social Security between Canada and the Kingdom of Norway.
PrecisOrder approving the TERMS AND CONDITIONS of the AGREEMENT ON SOCIAL SECURITY between Canada and the KINGDOM OF NORWAY, to implement changes to the Norwegian legislation that would increase the amount of a Norwegian benefit paid to its eligible recipients and to take into account changes in Canadian and Norwegian legislation which have occurred since the agreement was signed in 1985.
